*Para* je bila u rukama čoveka. (The money was in the man's hands.)

*Paru* je nosila u tašni. (She was carrying the money in her bag.)

On je imao *paru* za putovanje. (He had money for the trip.)

On je uložio *paru* u njegov biznis. (He invested money in his business.)

Ona je uložila više *para* u njenu školu. (She invested more money in her school.)

Oni su potrošili *paru* na kupovinu. (They spent money on shopping.)